-- PICC Group Says First-Half Profit Was Highest Insurer Has Had in `Years'
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-21T09:18:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-21/picc-group-says-first-half-profit-was-highest-insurer-has-had-in-years-.html

          
          
             PICC Group’s first-half profit was
the highest in “years,” according to an e-mailed statement
today. The company wasn’t more specific and it didn’t provide
profit numbers. Investment returns in the first half were
“basically stable.” PICC Group is the parent of Hong Kong-
listed PICC Property & Casualty Co.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Dingmin Zhang in Beijing at 
 dzhang14@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        